headline: Thanksgiving Travelers, Hurry Up and Wait. Expect Crowds and Bad Weather.
summary: AAA projects that a record 81.8 million people will travel at least 50 miles from home over the Thanksgiving holiday.

headline: Southwest Airlines (LUV): Evaluating Valuation Following Recent Modest Share Price Gains
summary: Southwest Airlines (LUV) shares made modest gains recently, rising about 3% over the past week and 10% in the past year. Investors are watching to see if the positive trend continues following a period of underperformance. See our latest analysis for Southwest Airlines.
